==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] [[Μικρονήσος]] (''Mikronesos'') "small island", from prefix [[μικρο-]] (''mikro-'') "micro-", from [[Ancient Greek]] [[μικρός]] (''mikros'') "small, mimimum" + [[νήσος]] (''nesos'') "island".

